src:
Office Depots resultat bättre än väntat under tredje kvartalet
Kontorsvaruleverantören Office Depot redovisar en omsättning som var något sämre än väntat under tredje kvartalet. Justerat resultat per aktie var däremot högre än väntat.
06 Nov 2019, 12:23 by FinWire

text:
Office Depot's earnings better than expected in the third quarter
Office supplies provider Office Depot reports sales that were slightly worse than expected during the third quarter. However, adjusted earnings per share were higher than expected.
06 Nov 2019, 12:23 by FinWire
